@startuml
title SAML Authentication and Default Role Assignment

|End-User|
start
:Access MAIKINE;
:Select login;

|Laravel (Service Provider)|
:Redirect user to UPRM login through SAML;

|UPRM Identity Provider|
:Authenticate user credentials;
if (Authentication successful?) then (Yes)
  :Return SAML assertion to Laravel;
else (No)
  :Deny authentication;
  stop
endif

|Laravel (Service Provider)|
:Validate SAML assertion;
:Extract user identity attributes;
:Search for local user account;
if (Account exists in MAIKINE?) then (Yes)
  :Load stored role;
else (No)
  :Create local user account;
  :Assign default role = user;
endif

:Authorize access based on role;
:Display permitted system dashboard;

end
@enduml